mission.mission: To support women through their fertility, pregnancy, and motherhood journeys while training others to become certified fertility coaches, creating a nurturing and professional environment for transformation.
mission.statement: Elizabeth King Coaching focuses on empowering women on their journey to motherhood through personalized fertility coaching and certification programs for aspiring fertility coaches.
mission.belief: Every woman deserves compassionate, professional guidance on her journey to motherhood.

quizTopics.title: What Type of Fertility Journeyer Are You?
quizTopics.description: Take this quick 2-minute quiz to discover your unique fertility personality and get personalized tips for your journey!

categories.name: The Intuitive Nurturer
categories.description: You naturally tune into your body's wisdom and prioritize self-care throughout your fertility journey.
categories.nextSteps: Focus on deepening your intuitive practices with our guided fertility meditation series.

categories.name: The Research-Driven Planner
categories.description: You thrive on information and prefer making fertility decisions based on thorough research and expert advice.
categories.nextSteps: Our evidence-based fertility tracking system was made for analytical minds like yours!

categories.name: The Balanced Optimizer
categories.description: You seek harmony between scientific approaches and emotional wellbeing on your path to conception.
categories.nextSteps: Our holistic fertility program combines medical insights with mindfulness practices just for you.

categories.name: The Community Builder
categories.description: You find strength in connection and value sharing experiences with others on similar fertility journeys.
categories.nextSteps: Join our supportive fertility circle where women like you share wisdom and encouragement.

quizTopics.title: What Kind of Mom Will You Be?
quizTopics.description: Curious about your motherhood style? Take this fun 5-question quiz to discover your natural parenting strengths!

categories.name: The Nurturing Guide
categories.description: You naturally create secure attachments and emotional safety, helping your child explore with confidence.
categories.nextSteps: Our attachment-focused motherhood preparation class will enhance your natural parenting style.

categories.name: The Playful Explorer
categories.description: You bring fun and creativity to motherhood, turning everyday moments into adventures and learning experiences.
categories.nextSteps: Check out our playful parenting workshop to build on your natural creativity as a mom.

categories.name: The Calm Anchor
categories.description: You create stability and peaceful routines, helping your child feel secure even during challenging transitions.
categories.nextSteps: Our mindful motherhood program will complement your natural ability to create calm.

categories.name: The Wise Teacher
categories.description: You naturally look for growth opportunities and love sharing knowledge with your child at every stage.
categories.nextSteps: Our developmental milestone guide will give you even more ways to nurture your child's learning.

quizTopics.title: Are You Making These 5 Fertility Mistakes Without Realizing It?
quizTopics.description: Discover if everyday habits might be affecting your fertility in this eye-opening 3-minute quiz!

mistakes.solution: Learn how our comprehensive fertility tracking system helps you identify your most fertile days with multiple indicators.
Discover our science-backed stress reduction techniques specifically designed for women on fertility journeys.

mistakes.mistake: Missing your body's natural fertility window
mistakes.solution: Our precision fertility coaching helps you identify and optimize your unique fertility patterns.

mistakes.mistake: Using products that disrupt hormonal balance
mistakes.solution: Get our free guide to fertility-friendly products and easy household swaps.

mistakes.mistake: Going through your fertility journey alone
mistakes.solution: Join our supportive community of women who understand exactly what you're experiencing.

quizTopics.title: Are You Making These 3 Mistakes That Keep You From Becoming a Successful Fertility Coach?
quizTopics.description: Take this quick quiz to uncover the common pitfalls preventing aspiring coaches from building thriving practices!

mistakes.solution: Learn our specialized fertility coaching framework developed through years of successful client work.

mistakes.mistake: Not knowing how to address the emotional aspects of fertility journeys
mistakes.solution: Our training includes advanced emotional support techniques specifically for fertility clients.
